4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students will learn essential tools such as Python, SQL, and statistics, and master the development of predictive models. The program includes three classes weekly with a maximum of 12 students per class, ensuring personalized attention. Students will work on real-life problems and gain hands-on experience with industry-standard tools, covering both supervised and unsupervised learning. Upon completion, graduates receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop